Reasoning: The paper deals with the downlink channel in wireless communication systems, specifically the MISO channel with constant envelope (CE) transmission. This falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the use of power-efficient RF amplifiers, which could fall under the sub-categories of signal processing (cs.SI) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper mentions the use of large antenna arrays, which could fall under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
